OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777676582
OL,3,CTeenager in custody after suspicious
OL,4,Cpackage found at Peter Kay gig
OL,6,FA Peter Kay gig has been evacuated
OL,7,Fafter a "potential suspicious bag" was
OL,8,Ffound, police say.
OL,10,FWest Midlands Police wrote on X that
OL,11,Fthe Utilita Arena in Birmingham was
OL,12,Fevacuated on Friday evening.
OL,14,FA 19-year-old man is in custody, and
OL,15,Fthe venue is being searched, the force
OL,16,Fadded.
OL,18,FThe comedian had been performing at
OL,19,Fthe venue on Friday evening.
OL,26,@oD@IOUoD@bO]
