OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777676582
OL,3,CTeenager in custody after suspicious
OL,4,Cpackage found at Peter Kay gig
OL,6,FThe Utilita Arena have put out a
OL,7,Fstatement saying: "Utilita Arena
OL,8,FBirmingham has been evacuated as a
OL,9,Fprecaution on the advice of West
OL,10,FMidlands Police after a potential
OL,11,Fsuspicious bag was found nearby.
OL,13,F"The safety and security of our
OL,14,Fcustomers and colleagues is our
OL,15,Fhighest priority.
OL,17,F"We can confirm everyone was safely
OL,18,Fevacuated and that the venue is secure.
OL,20,F"Ticket holders will be contacted
OL,21,Fdirectly in due course."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
