OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777676582
OL,3,CTeenager in custody after suspicious
OL,4,Cpackage found at Peter Kay gig
OL,6,FOn Thursday, the UK's terror threat
OL,7,Flevel was raised to "severe" in the
OL,8,Fwake of the Golders Green, meaning a
OL,9,Fterror attack is "highly likely".
OL,11,FThe Joint Terrorism Analysis Centre
OL,12,Fannounced the decision on Thursday, a
OL,13,Fday after two Jewish men were stabbed
OL,14,Fin north London and in the wake of
OL,15,Fseveral attacks in Jewish
OL,16,Fneighbourhoods in recent weeks.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
